description:
One unlucky astronaut has crash landed on a far-off planet, and now they need to find a way home. Solve puzzles with the help of a few little bugs to find a way off this rock!

Install Instructions:

Download the Backtrace Game Jam Files zip and extract all.

Run the Backtrace Game Jam.exe file located inside the folder.

If prompted with a warning, click more info and then ignore.

Enjoy the game
